doc.previous: The state is divided into three administrative regions Regierungsbezirke Kassel in the north and east Gie en in the centre and Darmstadt in the south the latter being the most populous region covering much of the Rhine Main agglomeration The administrative regions have no legislature of their own but are executive agencies of the state government
